<div dir="ltr"><span style="font-size:14px">Run MPI_Send on MPI1.8.5 without multithread enabled:</span><div style="font-size:14px">it hangs on mca_pml_ob1_send() -&gt; opal_progreses() -&gt; btl_openib_component_progress() -&gt; poll_device() -&gt; libmlx4-rdmav2.so -&gt; cq -&gt; phread_spin_unlock</div><div style="font-size:14px">The program can run on TCP with no error.</div></div>

